  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "AKS-74U Alfa Arms Goliaf M-LOK护木",
      "en": "AKS-74U Alfa Arms Goliaf M-LOK handguard"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Goliaf MLOK",
      "en": "Goliaf MLOK"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 30,000₽ | 物品价值: 5,194 | Mechanic报价: 2,909₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 6,752₽\n购买渠道 @ Skier 等级2 < 5,974₽\n\n以铝合金D16T为原料一体化量产的护木，经过了黑色涂层处理。能够替代AKS-74U的标准护木。在握把的两侧安装有M-LOK 导轨，可以在此基础上安装额外的配件（战术握把、手电筒、激光指示器等）。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 30,000₽ | 物品价值: 5,194 | Mechanic报价: 2,909₽购买渠道 @ Fence 等级1 < 6,752₽\n购买渠道 @ Skier 等级2 < 5,974₽\n\nThis integrally machined handguard can be installed instead of the standard-issue foregrip on the AKS-74U. It comes fitted with place for M-LOK rail mounts on three sides, allowing for the installation of additional equipment such as tactical foregrips, flashlights, and laser designators."
    },
